{"title":"2020S2D6T3","time_limit":1500,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期","图论"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1217#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1217","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1217/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1217/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1217"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"有权有向图 $G(n, m)$，有 $n$ 个节点和 $m$ 条边，节点编号 $1,2,\\cdots, n$。求所有其他节点到节点 $p$ 的最短往返路径中的最大值。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行三个正整数 $n, m, p$。\r\n\r\n接下来 $m$ 行，每行三个整数 $u_i, v_i, w_i$ ，分别表示一条有向边的起点，终点和权值。\r\n\r\n数据保证图是强连通的。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出一行一个整数，表示其他节点最短的往返路径中最长的长度。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n4 7 2\r\n1 3 2\r\n3 4 4\r\n4 2 3\r\n1 4 7\r\n1 2 4\r\n2 3 5\r\n3 1 2\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n12\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$2 \\le n \\le 10^3$\r\n\r\n$n \\le m \\le 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\le w_i \\le 100$"}]}